			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Shaman follow the same pattern of missing important types of damage.  We get no fire nukes or dots beyond level 1, and no magic nukes or dots other than the wimpy epic dot.  For cold, we have inefficient nukes, but no cold dots.  Poison and disease are our thing.  For us, if the mobs are essentially invulnerable to poison and disease (e.g., undead in Veksar), forget about them as a soloing target.
<br />

<br />
One of the most important improvements we know about from LDoN is the new Bane dot which will be our first Magic based dot.  Be nice if mages got something for Cold.<br />_________________<br />Roxxanne Redspirit
<br />
65 Prophet
<br />
Bertox</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
