			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">To be honest, I have no problem at all with Mages getting a Cold-based line of nukes.  Although we currently only have 2 lines of DDs (as do Mages) I don't think it will have much impact on the overall balance of the game.
<br />

<br />
However, if an increase in Mage flexibility would be in the works, a high damage bolt-like spell would be a nice Druid addition.  As it stands, we have no shot competing with Mages in the DPS department.  Not all of us are Alteration specced healers and it's quite discouraging to be outdamaged by a  Mage 5-10 levels lower =\
<br />

<br />
Overall, I wouldn't mind a cold-based line for Mages tho.
<br />

<br />
Elder Primero Aventuero
<br />
65 Druid</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
